SUMMARY:Information: WEAVER LINE: Sunday 15 March\, until 1015\, no service
  between Liverpool Street and Cheshunt / Chingford / Enfield Town. Use 
 VICTORIA LINE connections between Central London and Seven Sisters / 
 Walthamstow Central. Replacement buses operate. Liverpool Street National 
 Rail station will be closed all day\, and GREATER ANGLIA trains will not 
 call at Hackney Downs and Seven Sisters.
END:VEVENT
