SUMMARY:Information: WEAVER LINE: Sunday 15 March\, from 1015\, a reduced 
 service operates. Trains operate every 30 minutes between London Fields 
 and Chingford\, every hour between London Fields and Cheshunt\, and every 
 hour between London Fields and Enfield Town. There will be no service 
 to/from Liverpool Street\, Bethnal Green and Cambridge Heath all day. No 
 GREATER ANGLIA services call at Hackney Downs or Seven Sisters all day.
END:VEVENT
